1
00:00:54,159 --> 00:00:54,920
What are you doing?

2
00:00:55,359 --> 00:00:56,320
When you were watching just now,

3
00:00:56,399 --> 00:00:57,439
weren't you quite generous?

4
00:00:59,079 --> 00:01:00,200
Who wants to watch you?

5
00:01:00,320 --> 00:01:01,200
I don't even want to glance at you.

6
00:01:29,680 --> 00:01:30,680
Didn't you say you wouldn't look?

7
00:01:35,239 --> 00:01:36,359
Do you think you're special?

8
00:01:36,959 --> 00:01:37,719
I'm leaving now.

9
00:01:52,120 --> 00:01:52,760
Brother.

10
00:02:01,000 --> 00:02:02,000
I think she likes you,

11
00:02:02,959 --> 00:02:03,920
but only to a certain extent.

12
00:02:06,920 --> 00:02:07,480
That's enough.

13
00:02:11,840 --> 00:02:12,439
Have some tea?

14
00:02:13,919 --> 00:02:15,680
Why is it hot?

15
00:02:16,840 --> 00:02:17,520
Well,

16
00:02:18,240 --> 00:02:20,039
it's said that we should eat radish in winter and ginger in summer.

17
00:02:20,159 --> 00:02:21,319
We should drink hot tea in summer.

18
00:02:22,680 --> 00:02:24,240
I don't understand your stomach.

19
00:02:29,120 --> 00:02:30,159
Don't you want to drink hot tea?

20
00:02:31,800 --> 00:02:32,319
Are you sleepy?

21
00:02:33,400 --> 00:02:33,960
It can help you refresh.

22
00:02:45,439 --> 00:02:46,000
What's wrong with you?

23
00:02:46,639 --> 00:02:47,280
Are you not feeling well?

24
00:02:48,479 --> 00:02:49,039
I'm fine.

25
00:02:50,879 --> 00:02:51,479
That's fine.

26
00:02:52,120 --> 00:02:53,120
Measure her size later.

27
00:02:53,400 --> 00:02:54,560
Women's clothing takes a long time.

28
00:02:54,680 --> 00:02:55,639
It takes several hours.

29
00:02:56,000 --> 00:02:56,719
Wait a while.

30
00:02:57,120 --> 00:02:58,240
Several hours?

31
00:02:58,400 --> 00:02:58,960
Yes.

32
00:02:59,840 --> 00:03:00,319
No need.

33
00:03:00,439 --> 00:03:02,319
I'll just rent one later.

34
00:03:02,680 --> 00:03:03,719
I have work at the clinic.

35
00:03:05,400 --> 00:03:06,360
I'm in a hurry.

36
00:03:06,639 --> 00:03:07,599
Don't you drive anymore?

37
00:03:07,759 --> 00:03:08,599
Can you give me a ride?

38
00:03:13,599 --> 00:03:14,360
You want me to give you a ride?

39
00:03:17,120 --> 00:03:18,159
It's on your way.

40
00:03:18,319 --> 00:03:18,919
On my way?

41
00:03:37,319 --> 00:03:38,280
Seventy percent.

42
00:03:39,960 --> 00:03:40,919
What's seventy percent?

43
00:03:41,879 --> 00:03:42,520
Sugar content.

44
00:03:43,400 --> 00:03:45,039
Why is this latte seventy percent sweet?

45
00:03:45,800 --> 00:03:46,639
Too sweet.

46
00:03:46,879 --> 00:03:47,360
Is it?

47
00:03:48,719 --> 00:03:49,240
Let's go.

48
00:04:06,479 --> 00:04:07,280
Thank you, Doctor Lan.

49
00:04:09,719 --> 00:04:10,599
You're a good doctor.

50
00:04:12,280 --> 00:04:13,159
I didn't thank you for this.

51
00:04:14,400 --> 00:04:15,759
Thank you for taking me to see a doctor.

52
00:04:19,319 --> 00:04:21,800
I said it's on the way.

53
00:04:23,199 --> 00:04:24,319
Can you stay up less at night?

54
00:04:25,120 --> 00:04:26,680
Your stomach is sick,

55
00:04:27,240 --> 00:04:28,480
don't ruin my reputation, okay?

56
00:04:37,800 --> 00:04:38,319
What's wrong?

57
00:04:38,959 --> 00:04:39,480
Stomachache.

58
00:04:40,360 --> 00:04:40,759
Stomach...

59
00:04:42,120 --> 00:04:42,680
Here?

60
00:04:46,120 --> 00:04:46,680
How about this?

61
00:04:47,800 --> 00:04:48,560
Does it hurt here?

62
00:04:54,639 --> 00:04:55,160
Smile.

63
00:05:06,040 --> 00:05:06,920
Hello, Lin Hao.

64
00:05:09,680 --> 00:05:11,519
Have you finished the promotional video plan?

65
00:05:15,439 --> 00:05:16,000
Okay.

66
00:05:27,439 --> 00:05:27,959
Hello.

67
00:05:28,600 --> 00:05:29,279
Hello, brother.

68
00:05:29,680 --> 00:05:30,639
You're getting cocky.

69
00:05:30,839 --> 00:05:32,360
What about the thing I asked you to do?

70
00:05:33,680 --> 00:05:35,360
You'll know in a moment.

71
00:05:35,800 --> 00:05:36,800
I'll send you an address later.

72
00:05:37,040 --> 00:05:37,519
Okay.

73
00:05:38,680 --> 00:05:39,120
Okay.

74
00:05:51,480 --> 00:05:52,079
Lan Xiaochuan.

75
00:05:54,160 --> 00:05:55,079
Jin Caien.

76
00:05:55,600 --> 00:05:56,439
Why are you here?

77
00:05:56,920 --> 00:05:58,120
Are you shooting a promotional video?

78
00:05:59,000 --> 00:05:59,959
To promote the clinic?

79
00:06:00,519 --> 00:06:01,560
It's so boring.

80
00:06:02,439 --> 00:06:03,839
It's none of your business.

81
00:06:04,360 --> 00:06:04,839
I...

82
00:06:05,399 --> 00:06:06,079
Korean.

83
00:06:07,000 --> 00:06:08,240
What does it matter to Koreans?

84
00:06:08,360 --> 00:06:10,000
Koreans experiencing traditional Chinese medicine

85
00:06:10,240 --> 00:06:11,560
to experience traditional Chinese medicine.

86
00:06:20,959 --> 00:06:21,480
Lin Hao.

87
00:06:22,680 --> 00:06:23,199
Xiaochuan,

88
00:06:42,639 --> 00:06:44,000
thank you for your hard work this time.

89
00:06:44,399 --> 00:06:45,920
I'll draft the contract and send it to you.

90
00:06:46,079 --> 00:06:47,959
Let's sign the contract before we cooperate.

91
00:06:48,120 --> 00:06:48,560
Okay.

92
00:06:50,000 --> 00:06:50,639
Who is this?

93
00:06:50,639 --> 00:06:52,480
A Korean friend I want to add to the shot.

94
00:06:52,560 --> 00:06:53,120
Kim Chae-eun.

95
00:06:53,439 --> 00:06:55,199
Miss Kim, this is Lin Hao,

96
00:06:55,279 --> 00:06:56,199
my good friend,

97
00:06:56,439 --> 00:06:58,040
He's here to make a promotional video for our clinic.

98
00:06:58,800 --> 00:06:59,639
Lin Hao.

99
00:07:00,480 --> 00:07:01,079
Hello.

100
00:07:02,199 --> 00:07:02,800
Miss Jin.

101
00:07:03,360 --> 00:07:03,839
Nice to meet you.

102
00:07:04,720 --> 00:07:05,560
I'll order some food.

103
00:07:05,680 --> 00:07:07,000
Let's eat first.

104
00:07:12,399 --> 00:07:13,199
What are you doing here?

105
00:07:30,600 --> 00:07:31,600
My dear.

106
00:07:32,439 --> 00:07:33,480
Long time no see.

107
00:07:54,680 --> 00:07:56,120
You'll be back to China next week, right?

108
00:07:57,600 --> 00:07:58,519
You don't want me to go?

109
00:07:59,399 --> 00:08:01,120
I don't want to part with you.

110
00:08:02,160 --> 00:08:03,120
But

111
00:08:03,480 --> 00:08:05,319
you really need this job.

112
00:08:06,279 --> 00:08:06,839
It doesn't matter.

113
00:08:07,639 --> 00:08:08,319
For you,

114
00:08:09,279 --> 00:08:10,040
I'll stay in Seoul.

115
00:08:15,000 --> 00:08:15,879
We broke up for so long.

116
00:08:16,920 --> 00:08:18,319
It's not a coincidence

117
00:08:19,600 --> 00:08:20,399
to appear with Lan Xiaochuan.

118
00:08:22,000 --> 00:08:22,800
Not exactly.

119
00:08:26,279 --> 00:08:28,600
I see many photos of her

120
00:08:29,319 --> 00:08:30,600
on the photo wall.

121
00:08:34,600 --> 00:08:35,200
What do you want to do?

122
00:08:37,080 --> 00:08:38,159
I just want to see the girl you like.

123
00:08:38,879 --> 00:08:39,440
Can't I?

124
00:08:41,399 --> 00:08:42,240
But

125
00:08:43,960 --> 00:08:45,240
she doesn't seem to like you.

126
00:08:48,159 --> 00:08:49,120
That's my business.

127
00:08:51,240 --> 00:08:52,519
So you like to take the initiative.

128
00:08:53,960 --> 00:08:54,720
But

129
00:08:56,759 --> 00:08:58,440
I like to make trouble.

130
00:09:07,519 --> 00:09:08,759
Brother, she's here.

131
00:09:10,639 --> 00:09:11,799
You have a lipstick mark on your face.

132
00:09:14,080 --> 00:09:14,480
Come on.

133
00:09:15,159 --> 00:09:16,360
You two eat first, there's more coming.

134
00:09:27,480 --> 00:09:28,559
What's wrong? Toothache?

135
00:09:31,039 --> 00:09:32,120
I'm kidding you.

136
00:09:36,600 --> 00:09:37,399
What did she say?

137
00:09:39,279 --> 00:09:39,840
Nothing.

138
00:10:47,480 --> 00:10:48,120
For you,

139
00:10:49,000 --> 00:10:49,799
I'll stay in Seoul.
